Detailed Description

Class Definition CRO_ACCESS_REPORT for LLRP message RO_ACCESS_REPORT.

  • Document Reference LLRP Specification Section 13.1.2

  • Document Reference LLRP Specification Section 16.1.30

This message is issued by the Reader to the Client, and it contains the results of the RO and Access operations. The ROReportSpec and AccessReportSpec parameters define the contents and triggers for this message.

void LLRP::CRO_ACCESS_REPORT::assimilateSubParameters (  CErrorDetails *  pError  )  [virtual]
 

Assimilates the decoded sub-parameters into m_listAllSubParameters.

After fields are decoded, the CDecoder itself takes care of gathering the subparameters into m_listAllSubParameters. Once the end of the enclosing TLV (or message) is reached this assimilateSubParameters() function is called to create parameter refrences from the primary member variables.

Parameters:
[out] pError Error details for encoded stream
